n%20campaign%2C%20leaving%20donors%20and%20voters%20alike%20wondering%20what%20happens%20now%20to%20the%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20he'd%20raised%20to%20support%20his%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20campaign%20finance%20experts%20are%20split%20on%20how%20the%20intricacies%20of%20the%20law%20will%20need%20to%20play%20out%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%3A%20Democrats%20have%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c87cad7a-2d48-401e-bb4f-457bec387876%5C%22%3EBiden's%20war%20chest%20surrendered%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBiden's%20announcement%20came%20after%20nearly%20a%20month%20of%20sustained%20criticism%20about%20his%20ability%20to%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20nominee%20following%20his%20debate%20performance%20against%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20June%2027.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20debate%2C%20in%20which%20Biden%20rambled%20and%20repeatedly%20appeared%20to%20lose%20his%20train%20of%20thought%2C%20many%20Democratic%20leaders%20urged%20Biden%20to%20step%20aside%20to%20give%20the%20party%20its%20best%20chance%20at%20defeating%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Biden%20campaign%20said%20donor%20funds%20had%20surged%20after%20the%20debate%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Felection-biden-fundraising-democrats-8492425af85796ad77844b77db6d0f30%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%20reporting%20his%20reelection%20campaign%20raised%20%24264%20million%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20the%20year%20alone%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20%24240%20million%20cash%20on%20hand.%20Still%2C%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdemocratic-megadonors-biden-drop-out-list-reed-hastings-abigail-disney-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDemocratic%20megadonors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20Netflix%20cofounder%20Reed%20Hastings%20and%20Abigail%20Disney%2C%20pledged%20to%20withhold%20funds%20from%20the%20party%20until%20Biden%20dropped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20he%20has%2C%20there's%20a%20massive%20pot%20of%20money%20for%20Democrats%20to%20deal%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22acefc26d-1c6a-42fd-85e1-f18ca97960ea%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20Biden's%20money%20goes%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECampaign%20finance%20experts%20disagree%20on%20the%20specifics%20of%20what%20the%20Biden%20campaign%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20with%20its%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharles%20Spies%2C%20a%20Republican%20campaign%20finance%20law%20expert%2C%20argued%20in%20an%20opinion%20article%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fbiden-has-100-million-reasons-to-stay-in-election-finance-d8a2dfdf%3Fmod%3Dhp_opin_pos_1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Biden%20would%20have%20needed%20to%20formally%20accept%20the%20Democratic%20nomination%20for%20president%20before%20passing%20the%20campaign's%20existing%20funds%20to%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20as%20long%20as%20she%20remained%20on%20the%20ticket.%20Biden%20endorsed%20her%20shortly%20after%20announcing%20he%20was%20withdrawing%20from%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20without%20having%20accepted%20the%20nomination%2C%20Spies%20wrote%20that%20Biden%20becomes%20beholden%20to%20the%20Federal%20Election%20Campaign%20Act's%20rules%20regulating%20%26quot%3Bexcess%20campaign%20funds%26quot%3B%20and%20can%20no%20longer%20donate%20more%20than%20%242%2C000%20to%20any%20other%20candidate%2C%C2%A0including%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaurav%20Ghosh%2C%20the%20director%20of%20federal%20campaign%20finance%20reform%20at%20the%20Campaign%20Legal%20Center%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2F91-million-question-what-happens-bidens-campaign-money-2024-07-18%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2C%20as%20long%20as%20Harris%20remains%20in%20the%20race%2C%20she%20automatically%20has%20access%20to%20the%20campaign's%20shared%20funds%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0regardless%20of%20whether%20the%20pair%20had%20formally%20accepted%20the%20nomination%20or%20not%2C%20since%20both%20names%20appeared%20on%20the%20same%20campaign%20registration%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Spies%20and%20Ghosh%20noted%20that%20either%20way%2C%20there%20are%20workarounds.%20The%20Biden%20campaign%20can%20either%20refund%20its%20donors%2C%20Ghosh%20told%20Reuters%2C%20or%2C%20they%20agreed%2C%20the%20campaign%20can%20pass%20the%20money%20back%20to%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20McMillan%2C%20founder%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20Save%20Democracy%20in%20America%2C%20a%20nonpartisan%20campaign%20to%20end%20the%20influence%20of%20corporate%20and%20special%20interest%20money%20in%20politics%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it%20ultimately%20doesn't%20matter%20which%20expert%20was%20right%20about%20the%20formal%20nomination%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Biden%20didn't%20stay%20in%20the%20race%20long%20enough%20to%20accept%20it%2C%20and%20it%20wouldn't%20have%20made%20a%20difference%20if%20he%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegal%20challenges%20may%20arise%20over%20how%2C%20exactly%2C%20these%20types%20of%20scenarios%20should%20play%20out%2C%20but%20final%20determinations%20in%20those%20cases%20will%20ultimately%20be%20made%20long%20after%20the%20election%20is%20decided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20a%20nonargument%20because%20that%20money%20is%20not%20going%20to%20go%20to%20waste%2C%26quot%3B%20McMillan%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20other%20than%20Harris%20becomes%20the%20nominee%2C%20then%20the%20campaign%20will%20just%20give%20this%20money%20to%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Committee%20or%20to%20other%20party%20committees%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20those%20committees%20can%20then%20spend%20that%20money%20in%20ways%20that%20benefit%20the%20presidential%20campaign%20of%20other%20Democratic%20candidates.%20So%20the%20money's%20not%20going%20to%20go%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20funds%20are%20ultimately%20transferred%20to%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Committee%2C%20the%20party%20can%20then%20spend%20unlimited%20amounts%20on%20ads%20promoting%20a%20new%20candidate%20and%20up%20to%20%2432%20million%20directly%20on%20a%20new%20campaign.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20funds%20can%20be%20divvied%20up%20to%20other%20other%20action%20committees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhoever%20ends%20up%20as%20the%20Democratic%20nominee%2C%20McMillan%20noted%2C%20they'll%20have%20no%20shortage%20of%20financial%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20gonna%20make%20a%20huge%20difference%20in%20how%20the%20campaign%20is%20conducted%20in%20a%20meaningful%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20McMillan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-campaign-funds-after-he-dropped-out-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721587387000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669d568d2d66759f66fcb3d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-campaign-funds-after-he-dropped-out-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Joe%20Biden%20declared%20he's%20dropping%20out%20of%20his%20reelection%20campaign%2C%20prompting%20questions%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20millions%20in%20his%20war%20chest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-campaign-funds-after-he-dropped-out-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20Reacts%20to%20Joe%20Biden%20Dropping%20Out%20of%20Presidential%20Race%3A%20He%20Is%20%E2%80%98Certainly%20Not%20Fit%20to%20Serve%20%E2%80%94%20And%20Never%20Was%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721587270000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fva