em%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20we%20have%20made%20great%20progress%20as%20a%20Nation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EToday%2C%20America%20has%20the%20strongest%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%20We've%20made%20historic%20investments%20in%20rebuilding%20our%20Nation%2C%20in%20lowering%20prescription%20drug%20costs%20for%20seniors%2C%20and%20in%20expanding%20affordable%20health%20care%20to%20a%20record%20number%20of%20Americans.%20We've%20provided%20critically%20needed%20care%20to%20a%20million%20veterans%20exposed%20to%20toxic%20substances.%20Passed%20the%20first%20gun%20safety%20law%20in%2030%20years.%20Appointed%20the%20first%20African%20American%20woman%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20And%20passed%20the%20most%20significant%20climate%20legislation%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world.%20America%20has%20never%20been%20better%20positioned%20to%20lead%20than%20we%20are%20today.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EI%20know%20none%20of%20this%20could%20have%20been%20done%20without%20you%2C%20the%20American%20people.%20Together%2C%20we%20overcame%20a%20once%20in%20a%20century%20pandemic%20and%20the%20worst%20economic%20crisis%20since%20the%20Great%20Depression.%20We've%20protected%20and%20preserved%20our%20Democracy.%20And%20we've%20revitalized%20and%20strengthened%20our%20alliances%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20has%20been%20the%20greatest%20honor%20of%20my%20life%20to%20serve%20as%20your%20President.%20And%20while%20it%20has%20been%20my%20intention%20to%20see%20reelection%2C%20I%20believe%20it%20is%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20my%20party%20and%20the%20country%20for%20me%20to%20stand%20down%20and%20to%20focus%20solely%20on%20fulfilling%20my%20duties%20as%20President%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20my%20term.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3