0we're%20traveling%20more%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20I%20think%20we're%20more%20ready%20than%20ever%20to%20consider%20the%20implications%20of%20our%20travels.%20And%20actually%20surveys%20are%20showing%20that%20people%20are%20more%20concerned%20about%20sustainability%2C%20they're%20more%20concerned%20about%20their%20impacts%20on%20communities.%20They're%20willing%20to%20spend%20more%20to%20have%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20the%20place.%20So%20I%20hope%20the%20book%20is%20coming%20really%20at%20the%20right%20moment%20to%20speak%20to%20that%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20there%20a%20specific%20moment%20or%20an%20experience%20you%20had%20traveling%20that%20sparked%20the%20idea%20for%20the%20book%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20I%20moved%20with%20my%20family%20to%20a%20little%20village%20in%20the%20French%20Alps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20see%20firsthand%20how%20tourism%20really%20brought%20life%20into%20this%20village%20that%20would%20otherwise%20have%20become%20a%20ghost%20town%2C%20probably%2050%20years%20ago.%20It%20brought%20life%2C%20it%20brought%20energy%2C%20it%20brought%20culture%2C%20it%20brought%20all%20sorts%20of%20activities%20for%20my%20family%2C%20for%20me%20and%20my%20children%2C%20that%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20had%20otherwise%20in%20this%20beautiful%20corner%20of%20the%20French%20Alps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20as%20a%20resident%20of%20a%20tourist%20destination%2C%20I%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%2C%20really%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20things%20like%20having%20a%20heaving%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Egrocery%20store%20for%20maybe%20six%20or%20eight%20weeks%20a%20year%2C%20or%20having%20the%20parking%20lot%20where%20drop%20kids%20off%20at%20school%20overflowing%20sometimes%2C%20or%20sitting%20in%20bumper%20to%20bumper%20traffic%20on%20the%20road%20that%20leads%20to%20my%20house%20when%20I'm%20just%20trying%20to%20get%20home%20with%20my%20groceries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETourism%20is%20so%20huge%20and%20it%20has%20so%20many%20impacts%20that%20go%20so%20much%20deeper%20below%20the%20surface%20than%20most%20of%20us%20think%20about%20when%20we're%20traveling.%20It%20was%20really%20so%20moving%20to%20this%20village%20that%20that%20inspired%20me%20to%20start%20looking%20at%20travel%20and%20tourism%20in%20my%20journalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverywhere%20I%20look%2C%20there's%20complexities%2C%20there's%20good%20and%20bad%20and%20it's%20so%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20describe%20what%20you%20mean%20by%20%26quot%3Bthe%20new%20tourist%26quot%3B%3F%20What%20does%20a%20new%20tourist%20look%20like%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20chapter%20of%20the%20book%2C%20I%20respond%20to%20an%20essay%20that%20was%20written%20by%20an%20exceptional%20writer%20named%20Agnes%20Kard%20and%20published%20in%20The%20New%20Yorker%20last%20summer%20called%20%26quot%3BThe%20Case%20Against%20Travel.%26quot%3B%20She%20described%20some%20tourists%20as%20%26quot%3Bunchanged%20changers%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20people%20who%20go%20to%20a%20place%20and%20they%20change%20the%20place%2C%20they%20inflict%20their%20presence%20on%20the%20place%2C%20and%20they're%20unchanged.%20They%20themselves%20remain%20closed%20in%20their%20hearts%20and%20minds%20to%20the%20experience%20and%20they%20come%20away%20unmoved.%20So%2C%20I%20took%20that%20as%20my%20starting%20point.%20That's%20what%20I%20see%20as%20an%20old%20tourist.%20Let's%20have%20a%20new%20tourist%20be%20somebody%20who's%20a%20changed%20changer%2C%20changed%20and%20enlightened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20tourist%20is%20someone%20who%20takes%20the%20time%20to%20educate%20themselves%20about%20the%20impact%20that%20their%20presence%20will%20have%20on%20the%20place%20they're%20visiting%20and%20uses%20that%20knowledge%20to%20do%20their%20best%20to%20minimize%20any%20negative%20impacts%20of%20their%20presence%20on%20the%20place%20and%20maximize%20any%20positive%20impacts%2C%20whether%20it's%20economic%2C%20social%2C%20or%20cultural%20impacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they're%20changed%20themselves.%20They%20come%20with%20a%20view%20to%20having%20their%20mind%20changed.%20They%20come%20with%20a%20level%20of%20humility.%20They%20come%20with%20a%20strong%20desire%20to%20really%20see%20the%20humanity%20in%20the%20people%20they're%20visiting%20and%20the%20beauty%20in%20the%20place%20they're%20visiting%20and%20don't%20see%20themselves%20as%20superior%20to%20the%20people%20or%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20mindset%20shift%2C%20really%2C%20but%20I%20think%20that%20it's%20a%20really%20powerful%20mindset%20shift%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20very%20constructive%20impacts%20both%20the%20tourist%20destination%20and%20on%20the%20traveler%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20might%20travel%20look%20differently%20for%20someone%20who's%20embraced%20that%20mindset%3F%20How%20would%20their%20behaviors%20change%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20start%20as%20an%20example%2C%20how%20you%20decide%20where%20you're%20going%20to%20go%20on%20a%20trip.%20When%20you're%20thinking%20about%20where%20you%20want%20to%20go%2C%20really%20take%20some%20time%20to%20reflect.%20Are%20you%20going%20to%20a%20place%20because%20it's%20on%20some%20top%2010%20list%20that%20you%20saw%2C%20and%20you%20feel%20like%20you're%20obligated%20to%20cross%20it%20off%3F%20Or%20are%20you%20going%20for%20a%20deeper%20sort%20of%20reason%2C%20like%20you%20want%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20culture%3F%20Maybe%20there's%20something%20meaningful%20there%20that%20you%20want%20to%20take%20the%20time%20to%20really%20learn%20about%20or%20get%20engaged%20with%20when%20you're%20there.%20I%20think%20it%20starts%20with%20self-reflection%20and%20making%20sure%20your%20motivations%20for%20where%20you%20want%20to%20travel%20are%20coming%20from%20a%20deeper%20place%20and%20not%20a%20superficial%20bucket%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20really%20practical%20level%2C%20maybe%20taking%20fewer%20trips%2C%20but%20staying%20longer%20and%20really%20taking%20the%20time%20to%20engage%20in%20a%20place.%20Because%20if%20you%2C%20as%20an%20American%2C%20come%20to%20Europe%20for%20two%20weeks%20and%20hit%20five%20major%20cities%20with%20two%20to%20three%20days%20in%20each%20place%2C%20that's%20not%20going%20to%20give%20you%20the%20chance%20to%20engage%20in%20a%20meaningful%20way%20with%20anybody%20who%20lives%20there%20or%20with%20the%20culture%20and%20history%20of%20the%20place.%20But%20if%20you%20come%20to%20Paris%20for%20two%20weeks%2C%20you%20settle%20in%2C%20and%20you're%20seeing%20the%20same%20people%20at%20the%20corner%20shop%20every%20day%2C%20you're%20going%20back%20to%20the%20same%20bar%20at%20the%20corner%2C%20the%20same%20cafe%20at%20the%20corner%2C%20and%20you%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20build%20some%20relationships.%20You%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20really%20get%20to%20know%20this%20corner%20of%20Paris.%20You%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20explore%20beyond%20the%20top%20five%20things%20to%20do%20and%20explore%20other%20perspectives%20of%20the%20city%2C%20not%20just%20the%20clich%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisiting%20fewer%20places%20is%20also%20better%20for%20the%20climate%20and%20it's%20better%20for%20the%20economies%20of%20the%20places%20you're%20visiting%20because%20every%20tourist%20destination%20wants%20people%20to%20come%20and%20stay%20longer.%20Be%20a%20high-quality%20visitor.%20And%20hire%20a%20local%20tour%20guide%2C%20whether%20it's%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20half%20a%20day%20or%20a%20full%20day%2C%20or%20multiple%20days.%20It%20gives%20you%20a%20chance%20to%20really%20have%20a%20personal%2C%20human%2C%20one-on-one%20interaction%20with%20someone%20who%20lives%20in%20that%20place%2C%20and%20you're%20directly%20supporting%20a%20local.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20aims%20we%20can%20have%20as%20new%20tourists%3A%20to%20come%20away%20with%20a%20real%20human%20connection%20and%20not%20just%20photos%20for%20our%20Instagram%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20write%20in%20the%20book%20that%20the%20stigma%20around%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Btourist%26quot%3B%20needs%20to%20change.%20Why%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20problem%20with%20somebody%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20travel%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20a%20tourist%20when%20I%20travel%2C%20I'm%20a%20traveler%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20It's%20like%2C%20OK%2C%20sure%2C%20you're%20a%20traveler%2C%20but%20I%20want%20you%20to%20remember%20that%20you're%20a%20tourist%20too.%20If%20we%20dissociate%20ourselves%20from%20this%20phenomenon%20of%20tourism%20that%20means%20we%20don't%20feel%20any%20ownership%20over%20the%20problems%20that%20tourism%20presents.%20If%20tourism%20is%20something%20that%20only%20other%20people%20do%2C%20then%20why%20should%20we%20be%20bothered%20about%20the%20problems%20that%20come%20with%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20implicate%20ourselves%20in%20tourism%2C%20if%20we%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I'm%20a%20tourist%2C%26quot%3B%20then%20we%20might%20hopefully%20feel%20some%20ownership%20over%20the%20problems%20with%20tourism%20and%20we%20might%20be%20inspired%20to%20actually%20do%20something%20to%20change%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20if%20tourism%20is%20this%20thing%20that%20only%20other%20people%20do%2C%20and%20everyone%20in%20the%20world%2C%20all%20of%20us%20who%20are%20lucky%20enough%20to%20travel%2C%20see%20tourism%20as%20something%20that%20other%20people%20do%2C%20nothing's%20ever%20going%20to%20get%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstop-saying-traveler-not-tourist-new-tourist-book-paige-mcclanahan-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721584765000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669870e3fb2b6bedb05828c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstop-saying-traveler-not-tourist-new-tourist-book-paige-mcclanahan-2024-7%22%2C%22summary