rd%20groups%20and%20the%20disabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20had%20stepped%20up%20their%20protest%20when%20Hasina%20refused%20to%20meet%20their%20demands%2C%20citing%20the%20court%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20called%20the%20protesters%20%26quot%3Brazakar%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20offensive%20term%20for%20those%20accused%20of%20collaborating%20with%20Pakistan's%20army%20in%201971%20to%20betray%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20THE%20QUOTA%20SYSTEM%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntroduced%20in%201972%2C%20Bangladesh's%20quota%20system%20has%20gone%20through%20several%20changes%20since.%20When%20it%20was%20abolished%20in%202018%2C%2056%25%20of%20government%20jobs%20were%20blocked%20under%20various%20quotas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bulk%20covered%20groups%20such%20as%20freedom%20fighters'%20families%2C%20with%20women%20and%20those%20from%20underdeveloped%20districts%20receiving%20a%20share%20of%20a%20tenth%20each%2C%20with%205%25%20allotted%20to%20indigenous%20communities%2C%20and%201%25%20for%20the%20disabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesting%20students%20want%20all%20categories%20abolished%2C%20except%20the%20last%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20SPARKED%20THE%20VIOLENCE%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20turned%20violent%20last%20week%20following%20clashes%20between%20thousands%20of%20anti-quota%20demonstrators%20and%20members%20of%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20Hasina's%20Awami%20League%20party.%20Police%20fired%20rubber%20bullets%20and%20hurled%20sound%20grenades%20and%20tear%20gas%20to%20scatter%20protesters%20who%20also%20blocked%20railway%20tracks%20and%20major%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20DO%20THE%20STUDENTS%20FEAR%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHasina%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%2C%20the%20founding%20father%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20who%20led%20its%20freedom%20movement.%20Protesters%20and%20critics%20say%20the%2030%25%20q