%20amount%2C%20subject%20to%20successful%20recovery%20and%20verification.%20%26quot%3BThis%20could%20potentially%20amount%20to%20%2423%20million%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20bounties%20ever%20offered%20in%20the%20crypto%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20crypto%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20foremost%20goal%20is%20to%20recover%20the%20stolen%20funds.%20This%20bounty%20programme%20is%20designed%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20expertise%20of%20the%20community%20to%20achieve%20this%20critical%20objective%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nischal%20Shetty%2C%20Founder%2C%20WazirX.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bounty%20programme%20will%20be%20active%20for%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cyber%20attack%2C%20which%20occurred%20on%20July%2018%2C%20resulted%20in%20%24234%20million%20being%20stolen%20from%20the%20WazirX%20multisig%20Ethereum%20Wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20December%2C%20the%20crypto%20exchange%20WazirX%20saw%20its%20trading%20volume%20nosedive%20to%20%241%20billion%20in%202023%20--%20a%20massive%2090%20per%20cent%20drop%20from%202022%20--%20amid%20regulatory%20pressure%20from%20the%20government%20and%20a%20heavy%20crypto%20tax%20regime.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20introduced%20a%2030%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20virtual%20currencies%20and%20a%201%20per%20cent%20deduction%20for%20every%20crypto%20transaction.%20In%20the%20same%20year%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20investigated%20several%20cases%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%202002%20(PMLA)%20and%20the%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%2C%201999%20(FEMA)%20related%20to%20cryptocurrencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721575800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F6l4tmnuo_cyb