2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dozens%20of%20illnesses%20across%2028%20states%20are%20now%20linked%20to%20a%20company's%20'microdosing'%20gummies%20and%20chocolate%20bars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224515%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Orange%20gummies%20next%20to%20clear%20bottle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669c0c82fb2b6bedb058f50e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223015%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20CDC%20published%20a%20report%20on%20%26quot%3Bmushroom%20gummies%26quot%3B%20sold%20in%20Virginia.%20%3Cp%3EDouglas%20Sacha%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOver%20five%20dozen%20people%20reported%20seeking%20medical%20attention%20after%20consuming%20Diamond%20Shruumz%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20study%20also%20found%20some%20of%20the%20company's%20gummies%20contained%20psilocin%2C%20a%20controlled%20substance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20FDA%20reported%2036%20hospitalizations%20and%20one%20potential%20death%20associated%20with%20the%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDiamond%20Shruumz%2C%20the%20company%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrodosing-chocolate-bar-diamond-shruumz-illness-hospital-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicrodosing%20chocolate%20bars%3C%2Fa%3E%20prompted%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Foutbreaks-foodborne-illness%2Finvestigation-illnesses-diamond-shruumz-brand-chocolate-bars-cones-gummies-june-2024%3Futm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Dgovdelivery%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFDA%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%2C%20has%20also%20sold%20gummies%20made%20with%20an%20illegal%20substance%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fmmwr%2Fvolumes%2F73%2Fwr%2Fmm7328a3.htm%23T1_down%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20CDC%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20first%20alerted%20the%20general%20public%20about%20Diamond%20Shruumz%20products%20after%20eight%20people%20in%20four%20states%20fell%20ill%20from%20consuming%20the%20retailer's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Foutbreaks-foodborne-illness%2Finvestigation-illnesses-diamond-shruumz-brand-microdosing-chocolate-bars-june-2024%3Futm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Dgovdelivery%23product%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicrodosing%20chocolate%20bars%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20now%20says%20that%20as%20of%20July%2015%2C%20those%20numbers%20have%20ballooned%20to%2069%20illnesses%20across%2028%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSixty%20(60)%20of%20the%2069%20people%20have%20reported%20seeking%20medical%20care%2C%2036%20have%20been%20hospitalized%2C%20and%20there%20is%20one%20potentially%20associated%20death%20under%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FDA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrodosing-psilocybin-mushrooms-for-creativity-startups-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrodosing%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20practice%20of%20taking%20small%20doses%20of%20a%20drug%2C%20typically%20psychedelics%20like%20psilocybin%2C%20to%20improve%20creativity%20and%20mental%20health.%20Microdosing%20has%20become%20trendy%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrodose-magic-mushrooms-increase-productivity-at-work-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeven%20among%20CEOs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiamond%20Shruumz's%20website%20said%20its%20products%20do%20not%20contain%20psilocybin%20or%20any%20other%20scheduled%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20tests%20conducted%20by%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia%20Health%20Toxicology%20Laboratory%20found%20psilocin%20in%20Diamond%20Shruumz's%20Sour%20Peach%20Apple%20and%20Rainbow%20gummies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPsilocin%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpsychedelic%20mushroom%20alkaloid%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.t3db.ca%2Ftoxins%2FT3D2458%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Metabolomics%20Innovation%20Centre%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20DEA%20considers%20psilocin%20a%20Schedule%20I%20controlled%20substance%20in%20some%20states%2C%20including%20Virginia%2C%20where%20the%20study%20was%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CDC%20study%20said%20five%20people%20underwent%20hospital%20evaluations%20between%20September%202023%20and%20June%202024%20after%20eating%20gummies%20labeled%20to%20contain%20Amanita%20muscaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Amanita%20muscaria%20can%20sometimes%20cause%20undesired%20symptoms%2C%20the%20report%20said%20it's%20legal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPersons%20who%20purchase%20products%20advertised%20as%20psychedelic%20or%20nootropic%20mushroom%20gummies%20should%20be%20aware%20that%20package%20labels%20might%20not%20accurately%20represent%20the%20contents%20and%20that%20these%20products%20could%20contain%20substances%20that%20might%20produce%20unexpected%20and%20potentially%20toxic%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Diamond%20Shruumz%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia%20Health%20Toxicology%20Laboratory%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiamond%20Shruumz%20recalled%20all%20of%20its%20products%20%E2%80%94%20including%20its%20gummies%20and%20chocolate%20bars%20%E2%80%94%20in%20June%20after%20illnesses%20continued%20to%20rise%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20it%20would%20monitor%20Prophet%20Premium%20Blends%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20Diamond%20Shruumz%2C%20during%20its%20recall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsumers%20should%20not%20purchase%20or%20consume%20any%20Diamond%20Shruumz-brand%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrodosing-gummies-chocolate-bars-diamond-shruumz-sick-f