ony%20in%20May.%3Cp%3EGIORGIO%20VIERA%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Trump%20campaign%20is%20calling%20out%20the%20Secret%20Service%20over%20security%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20campaign%20official%20said%20the%20service%20tried%20to%20block%20a%20Trump%20team%20request%20for%20metal%20detectors%20at%20Barron%20Trump's%20graduation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20lack%20of%20metal%20detectors%20at%20Trump%20events%20is%20a%20constant%20source%20of%20stress%2C%20the%20official%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Trump%20campaign%20official%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F07%2F20%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fsecret-service-trump-shooting.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20metal%20detectors%20to%20screen%20Trump%20event%20attendees%20had%20been%20a%20constant%20source%20of%20stress%20for%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20that%20the%20Secret%20Service%20had%20even%20tried%20to%20deny%20a%20request%20from%20Trump's%20team%20to%20install%20metal%20detectors%20at%20his%20son%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-attend-son-barron-high-school-graduation-after-all-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarron%20Trump's%20high%20school%20graduation%20in%20May%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20former%20president%20attended%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Melania.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20told%20The%20Times%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffemale-secret-service-agent-how-to-become-job-qualifications-dei-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESecret%20Service%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20graduation%20was%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%26quot%3B%20event%20before%20eventually%20caving%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20also%20noted%20that%20at%20one%20Trump%20rally%20in%20New%20York%20City%20in%20May%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20metal%20detectors%20created%20a%20backlog%20of%20people%20trying%20to%20enter%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20as%20the%20service%20went%20back%20on%20a%20statement%20saying%20that%20it%20had%20not%20turned%20down%20requests%20from%20Trump's%20team%20for%20additional%20federal%20resources%20in%20the%20two%20years%20prior%20to%20the%20assassination%20attempt%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecret%20Service%20spokesperson%20Anthony%20Guglielmi%20previously%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20an%20untrue%20assertion%20that%20a%20member%20of%20the%20former%20president's%20team%20requested%20additional%20resources%20and%20that%20those%20were%20rebuffed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Guglielmi%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20Service%20had%20indeed%20rejected%20some%20requests%20for%20additional%20security%20resources%2C%20but%20these%20denials%20were%20not%20specifically%20for%20the%20Butler%20event%2C%20The%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20The%20Times%2C%20Guglielmi%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20some%20instances%20where%20specific%20Secret%20Service%20specialized%20units%20or%20resources%20were%20not%20provided%2C%20the%20agency%20made%20modifications%20to%20ensure%20the%20security%20of%20the%20protected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20may%20include%20utilizing%20state%20or%20local%20partners%20to%20provide%20specialized%20functions%20or%20otherwise%20identifying%20alternatives%20to%20reduce%20public%20exposure%20of%20a%20protectee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Service%20has%20faced%20intense%20scrutiny%20since%20the%20Butler%20assassination%20attempt%2C%20during%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-was-thomas-matthew-crooks-the-trump-rally-shooter-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20-year-old%20Thomas%20Matthew%20Crooks%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Bethel%20Park%2C%20PA%2C%20was%20able%20to%20scale%20a%20warehouse%20roof%20armed%20with%20an%20AR-15-style%20rifle%20and%20open%20fire%20at%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20already%20having%20raised%20concerns%20about%20someone%20acting%20suspiciously%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrooks%20managed%20to%20position%20himself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgunman-450-feet-away-from-trump-when-he-fired-shots%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20around%20450%20feet%20away%20from%20where%20the%20former%20president%20was%20speaking%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20bullet%20struck%20Trump's%20right%20ear.%20One%20person%20was%20killed%2C%20and%20two%20were%20critically%20injured%20during%20the%20incident.%20Crooks%20was%20killed%20by%20a%20Secret%20Service%20sniper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20McCarthy%2C%20a%20former%20Secret%20Service%20agent%20who%20defended%20former%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan%20from%20a%20gunman%20in%201981%2C%20told%20Chicago-based%20outlet%20WGN-TV%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freagan-secret-service-agent-says-trump-shooting-failure-for-agency-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eassassination%20attempt%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20clear%20%26quot%3Bfailure%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20security%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20failure.%20Plain%20and%20simple%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAny%20time%20a%20protectee%20is%20harmed%2C%20there's%20something%20that%20has%20to%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%20has%20since%20said%20that%20Congress%20would%20be%20conducting%20an%20investigation%20into%20security%20at%20the%20rally%20%26quot%3Bto%20determine%20where%20there%20were%20lapses%20in%20security%20and%20anything%20else%20that%20the%20American%20people%20need%20to%20know%20and%20deserve%20to%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKimberly%20Cheatle%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Secr