betterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-34-1-1721126368.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-34-1-1721126368-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-34-1-1721126368-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-34-1-1721126368-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-34-1-1721126368-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357113%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETejas%20manages%20his%20full-time%20job%20and%20travelling%20along%20with%20his%20wife.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20college%2C%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20become%20an%20IT%20professional.%20But%20then%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20and%20we%20got%20to%20work%20from%20home.%20My%20girlfriend%20(now%20wife)%20and%20I%20started%20taking%20small%20trips%20around%20Managluru%20when%20the%20restrictions%20eased%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Tejas%20already%20had%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20where%20he%20did%20some%20moto-vlogging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20creating%20content%2C%20dedicating%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20each%20day%20to%20filming%20and%20editing.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20planned%20journey%20to%20becoming%20content%20creators%3B%20it%20just%20happened%20as%20we%20kept%20making%20videos%20and%20some%20of%20them%20went%20viral%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20he%20manages%20travelling%20with%20his%20full-time%20job%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20challenging%2C%20but%20we%20manage%20by%20prioritising%20travel%20over%20other%20activities.%20Both%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20have%20flexible%20jobs%20that%20allow%20us%20to%20work%20from%20anywhere.%20We%20have%20supportive%20managers%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20get%20time-off%20when%20needed.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%E2%80%99re%20travelling%2C%20we%20wake%20up%20early%2C%20explore%20the%20place%2C%20and%20then%20start%20working%20around%2011%20am.%20We%20work%20until%20about%206pm%2C%20take%20small%20breaks%20in%20between%2C%20and%20then%20spend%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20editing%20videos%20at%20night.%20It%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20prioritising%20travel%20and%20making%20the%20most%20of%20our%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20travelled%20to%20most%20states%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20initial%20goal%20was%20to%20cover%20ten%20states%20in%20a%20year.%20Recently%2C%20we%20went%20from%20Mangaluru%20to%20Srinagar.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20covered%20almost%20all%20the%20central%20states%2C%20taking%20about%20a%20month%20to%20explore%20each%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20covered%20most%20states%20except%20for%20five%20in%20the%20Northeast%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346358%2Fbest-homestays-in-western-ghats-for-a-summer-getaway-goa-panchgani-list-2024%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20the%20Western%20Ghats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Overall%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20covered%20nearly%20all%20the%20states%20on%20our%20bike%20except%20for%20a%20few%20regions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6d702PPYWZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6d702PPYWZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig